articles.title: Pics: Once Asia's Most Eligible Bachelor, Brunei Prince Marries A Commoner - NDTV
articles.description: In real life he's a prince of an Islamic sultanate steeped in centuries-old traditions, but on Instagram Brunei's Abdul Mateen is more Hollywood than royalty as he flies in fighter jets, drives speed boats and poses bare-chested after workouts.
articles.content:
He is unlikely to ever ascend the throne of the oil-rich country.
